{"tid":158848,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[我睇緊d乜] 動口不動手？好惡心呀！","createTime":"2017-03-16T14:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:55.000Z","uid":81082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1223588a85a16da49e51cfff82b8cfbfe66561d3","tid":158848,"uid":81082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170316/bkncn-20170316134634541-0316_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170316%2Fbkncn-20170316134634541-0316_05011_001.html&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=0cf2e5ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170316/bkncn-20170316134634541-0316_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n常言道：「君子動口不動手。」內地兩名男子近日在街頭發生爭執時，便充分表現出這種「美德」。網上瘋傳一段兩人爭吵的短片，片中兩名男子吵得十分激動，當途人都以為兩人快要大打出手之際，兩人竟開始互放「飛劍」，當街打起名副其實的「口水戰」。<br />\n<br />\n從短片可見，兩名男子當時俱手抱胸前，連珠炮發向對方臉部狂吐口水，鬥得難分難解。片刻之後，身材較高的男子見僵持不下，首先跳起來，向對手的臉部施以「空襲」。而較矮的男子開始節節敗退，最後無力為繼，最終都要出手將對方推開，拿出一瓶飲料喝了一口後便敗陣離場。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民看後都笑得合不攏嘴，留言稱：「這才是真正的君子之爭」、「這爭吵感覺好歡樂」、「隔着螢幕都能聞口水的臭味」、「這比試看似克制，其實暗藏殺機」。另有人直斥兩人的舉動惡心，指他們毫無衞生意識，「看得我都想洗臉了」。"},{"pid":"fb24528ce36ae1e566f62d342d264a1ecf1b6a0d","tid":158848,"uid":23998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e307c9aeefc4973284c44eef531d08db4d1eab","tid":158848,"uid":81082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑到肚痛"},{"pid":"92a0d00af7b0c39510bdabce7924758c0f13ef94","tid":158848,"uid":81082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}